![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b579ab3f-483e-42a6-8189-10c751d8aabe/20240607_171523.jpg)

Smackdown opens with Paul Heyman saying Solo has anointed Tama Tonga as "The Right Hand Man."

Big "WE WANT ROMAN" chants again.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4e948ab8-0460-4975-a3b4-5323e16ce4cb/20240607_171527.jpg)

Heyman also says Solo has anointed "The Infamous" Tonga Loa has a full fledged member of The Bloodline.

Kevin Owens comes out to brawl w/The Bloodline, but the numbers get the better of him until the Street Profits make the save.

KO grabs a steel chair and starts swinging to lead to The Bloodline bailing.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/de5f0d53-94ea-479f-b95d-bb808d11948e/20240607_171816.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/77297307-6db1-4332-979e-b7930695a96c/Screenshot_20240607_172722.jpg)

Backstage, Solo Sikoa tells Paul Heyman to get a 6 man tag made between Street Profits and Kevin Owens vs the Bloodline.

Otherwise the main event tonight will be Heyman vs Tama Tonga in the locker room(?!)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4e7b6a8e-9df9-4854-83ce-a65a86ccc215/Screenshot_20240607_172511.jpg)

Candice LeRae is no longer injured and complaining that Jade bullied Indi into a match this week.

Nick Aldis says the match is now a tag team match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d940f20c-7e2b-498b-a92c-b1419a3d944f/20240607_172656.jpg)

*   ## **_BIANCA BELAIR AND JADE CARGILL VS INDI HARTWELL AND CANDICE LERAE_**
    

As soon as the bell rings, Shayna Baszler, Zoey Starks appear on one side of the Ring. Isla Dawn and Alba Fyre appear on the other.

As soon as Jade and Bianca win the match, all hell breaks loose. A brawl breaks out in the ring amongst Shayna/Zoey and Isla/Alba. Jade and Bianca are taken out. The other two teams brawl. Jade and Bianca get back up and take out the “Unholy Union”

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6c19e4ad-a4fe-47b1-b604-2246f5316880/20240607_173413.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0eba7047-2661-4806-8bd2-fde13c5513a0/20240607_173352.jpg)

Cody Rhodes is furiously pacing back and forth waiting for AJ Styles to arrive at the arena. Aldis tries to calm him down hut Cody wants a fight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/64be5ee5-ffe0-4b76-9a86-d87a0acf478b/20240607_174231.jpg)

Apollo Crews is a out to cut a promo when he’s jumped by Legado De Phantasma

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e97b6a42-30e1-4839-a6ae-9fb51666d906/20240607_174235.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/040db3e6-efcd-4056-bf5e-43589e37b9c0/20240607_174242.jpg)

LA Knight is looking for Logan Paul who’s still not here. Carmello Hayes walks up and insults LA Knight in front of Nick Aldis who sets up a match between the two tonight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7c89ae43-fa97-46d8-8808-53e7b90b4ea7/20240607_174947.jpg)

*   ## **_GRAYSON WALLER DEF. JOHNNY GARGANO_**
    

Scary moment early on where Johnny Gargano does a sliced bread #2 on the outside and almost lands on his own head. Match ends when Grayson Waller pulls Austin Theory into the path of danger to give himself the advantage over Gargano.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6d793d3a-0d17-4024-928a-7191f9f82ad0/20240607_175817.jpg)

AJ Styles finally arrives to the building but Nick Aldis and security won’t let Cody get to AJ. Cody decides to head to the ring and call AJ Styles out directly.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5ce5e1a7-f275-4762-881c-8a4f8c30054b/20240607_180039.jpg)

Cody is ON FIRE. He screams for AJ to come to the ring. Styles comes out. He says Cody knows what he wants. “GIMME WHAT I WANT” a WWE Championship match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2f3c8f45-4f85-4857-b126-75b3d3e0843c/20240607_180139.jpg)

Cody is furious and he agrees to the match. But Cody wants to make AJ Styles say what he should’ve said last week. I QUIT

CODY RHODES VS AJ STYLES

CLASH AT THE CASTLE

I QUIT MATCH

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ac572445-9ac4-4280-9a4d-f22e80ac7374/20240607_180416.jpg)

Cody takes out security to get to AJ but they hold him back. AJ takes advantage and knocks Cody in the head while he’s held back.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a51538d7-1fd2-4d61-ade2-0f0c16d0ff6f/20240607_181408.jpg)

Bianca Belair and Jade Cargill will defend the Women’s Tag Team Championships against Isla Dawn/Alba Fyre and Shayna/Zoey at Clash at the Castle

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d876fc92-0a62-46be-b1fa-2f9a0813d194/20240607_181534.jpg)

*   # **_LA KNIGHT DEF. CARMELLO HAYES_**
    

After the match, Knight grabs a headset from the announcers.

“If you don’t wanna come to SmackDown, I’ll bring SmackDown to you”

— LA Knight to Logan Paul

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/603f7bca-3b97-45c4-ab1d-c1cb21cb0bbb/20240607_182301.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/89c85525-175e-44ef-8fdf-343f2fb8c4cf/20240607_182225.jpg)

Tiffany Stratton tells Nia Jax she was her second favorite choice to win Queen of the Ring behind herself.

She wants to partner with Nia. Queen of the Ring and Princess of the Ring.

She leaves Nia to think about it when Mia Yim walks up and they start to brawl. Nia slips on the slippery floor twice.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c85c2dfe-1ff4-4a0c-aedf-22f114c8dc6a/20240607_183637.jpg)

Great promo from both ladies here.

Bayley comes out. She doesn’t get to say much before Piper Niven and Chelsea inturrupt.

Bayley tells Piper she’s watched her journey and she respects all the things she’s done to get to WWE and stay there. Bayley understands how it feels to finally get a World Championship match in front of your friends and family. She would have given Piper a match if she had just asked.

But Bayley also knows what it’s like to lose in front of you friends and family. And that’s the experience she’s going to give Piper

Piper says all those words would mean something if Bayley knew anything about her journey. Piper is going to demolish Bayley and take the World Title. She hopes all the respect Bayley has for her will make it easier to stare at the lights as Piper takes her title.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/43a8c7e7-916e-4abb-82ed-7f2578383023/Screenshot_20240607_183656.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3b28da12-eddd-4c7d-9984-e74d15fa71d1/20240607_184912.jpg)

*   ## **_KEVIN OWENS AND THE STREET PROFITS_** DEF. THE BLOODLINE BY DQ
    

Super hot crowd for this match. Sick spot by Montez Ford where he leaps over the turnbuckle and lands on the other 5 men.

Match ends when Solo Sikoa starts using a steel chair. The Bloodline take the advantage then Solo starts using Roman Reigns moves to finish his enemies.

Solo has Tama and Tanga hold up Montez for a spear. Then the three men deliver a Shield Powerbomb to Kevin Owens to close the show.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a8227844-f0ec-434d-88d6-e3738b0b558e/Screenshot_20240607_185805.jpg)

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e1cc4fb9-ed32-49b8-be62-61d186139958/Screenshot_20240607_185825.jpg)

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/58a23ce4-6f74-4dfb-aa39-dda7d7845ce9/Screenshot_20240607_185909.jpg)